- id: '2069081051734167881'
  text: 'Fortnite Discovery blocked my island from its initial content testing because
    another creator updated their island and got into the New and Updated rows first.
    They ended up claiming the game title, even though it was available when I published.
    I released my game a day before their update, but they were pushed into the rows
    before I was.


    I worked on this game for months in my spare time. Seeing it dead on launch because
    of bad luck and the way Discovery works sucks pretty hard, especially after investing
    time and money into it.


    @FNCreate @Flak #UEFN'
