- id: '2068928370113643002'
  text: "This is bit of a personal gripe for me. When I started my applications for\
    \ graduate and masters schools, it was so overwhelming. There's GRE, TOEFL, SOPs,\
    \ LORs etc and every country's (and even different universities in the same country)\
    \ application seems to follow some different procedures and guidelines. \n\nI\
    \ felt a bit lost there. \n\nSo I decided to try out consulting agencies. But\
    \ they didn't have a clue about what I am trying to do and wanted to push me towards\
    \ universities I had no interest in applying to (I am guessing they were getting\
    \ commissions). \nSeeing the lack of value and exorbitant costs I decided not\
    \ to go with any consulting agency. It was not worth it. \n\nBut I was still overwhelmed\
    \ and needed clarity. After asking a lot of questions from my seniors and peers,\
    \ reading countless guides, reddit threads, youtube videos, making dozens of spreadsheets,\
    \ and 6-8 months of hustle, things started to make sense. \n\nMy mails were getting\
    \ better, my SOPs were not generic and had clarity and gradually professors started\
    \ showing interest in my cold emails. \n\nThen I realised that this whole journey\
    \ is not impossible, just very confusing and overwhelming for those who have just\
    \ started. And the study abroad consulting industry is a big elaborate scam. \n\
    \nThat's when I decided to set my eyes on how to fix this problem (one I had faced\
    \ and suffered personally from). \n\nTogether with @Aryann_7, I am happy to announce\
    \ that we are starting Enrolia Private Beta Cohort, completely free for the whole\
    \ application cycle, for students who want to study abroad, but don't have the\
    \ luxury to go with expensive consulting agencies. \nWe will help all students/applicants\
    \ in gaining the confidence to apply, write cold emails that gets replies, draft\
    \ stellar SOPs, apply for scholarships, shortlist universities and professors\
    \ that are fit for them. On top we are not taking commissions from any university,\
    \ ever!\nWe will have weekly sessions over discord and solve all doubts asynchronously\
    \ in the channels. Also we will bringing a lot of current students and alumni\
    \ from top schools to solve student's doubts. \n\nPeople who are genuinely in\
    \ need of something like this and are ready to put it in the effort are welcome\
    \ to apply. We will not hand hold but actually teach the applicants how to traverse\
    \ through this whole process without feeling overwhelmed, and if they get stuck,\
    \ we are there to help them. \n\nDue to limited manpower, we can only open up\
    \ this cohort for upto 250 students in this cycle.\n\nVisit https://t.co/eUM5tKxIKZ\
    \ to apply. We will be reading each and every application manually. \n\nFor others,\
    \ please spread the word, so that this post reaches to students who are genuinely\
    \ in need. Students who otherwise would give up on their dreams to study abroad."
